1) user input a character

	a->"you have enter a"
	
	b->"you have enter b"
	
	c->"you have enter c"
	
	->Invalid character


2)user input a number

	positive number
		odd number
			perform addition with an integer constant
	
		even number
			perform multiplication with an floating point constant
	
	negative number
		odd number
			perform subtraction with an integer constant
		
		even number
			perform division with an floating point constant

3)user input marks

	90 to 100->A grade
	
	80 to 90->B grade
	
	60 to 80->C grade
	
	40 to 60->D grade
	
	< 40     ->Fail
	
	>100 	->Invalid Marks

